Minimum Y level for Bogged spawns
Minimum Y level for bogged spawns, for example 62 means that bogged will spawn only above the ocean Y level.
Spawn chance of Bogged
Spawn chance of bogged, for example 80% means that bogged will spawn in place of 80% of all skeletons spawned in swamp biomes.
Chance of Bogged spawners in dungeons
Chance of bogged spawner in dungeons, for example 80% means that bogged spawner will be in place of 80% of all skeleton spawners in swamp biomes.

Enable better Bogged spawns
